%% Evidence: MRA-E008, MRA-E009, MRA-E004, MRA-E014
sequenceDiagram
  participant Admin
  participant Page as Admin reports UI
  participant Action as resolveReportAndRemoveListing
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant Audit as AuditLog

  Admin->>Page: Resolve report and remove listing
  Page->>Action: reportId and notes
  Action->>Action: require admin and admin-delete rate limit
  Action->>DB: Lock Report FOR UPDATE
  Action->>DB: Lock Listing FOR UPDATE
  Action->>DB: Resolve report and pause listing with SUPPRESSED
  Action->>DB: Mark listing dirty and sync lifecycle
  Action->>Audit: Log REPORT_RESOLVED
  Action->>Audit: Log LISTING_HIDDEN
  Action-->>Page: success
